<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title, description }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-page text-text-primary font-body antialiased overflow-x-hidden">
  <canvas id="dot-grid" class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div id="cursor-glow" class="fixed w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 pt-20">
    <section class="py-section-sm lg:py-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">You're In</span>
        <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">Welcome to the 75 Hard AI Challenge.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Your signup is saved. The next step is to join the community, where the challenge instructions, tutorials, updates, and Day 1 resources will live.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm lg:pb-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-12 text-center" data-tilt>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Next Step</span>
          <h2 class="mt-5 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Join the Skool community.</h2>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            This is where you will find the videos, tutorials, challenge guidance, and practical next steps for getting started. Join now so you have the community and resources ready before Day 1.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="https://www.skool.com/75-hard-ai-3646/about" class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>
              Join the Community
            </a>
            <a href="/75-hard-ai-challenge" class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-border-subtle px-8 py-4 text-text-secondary font-semibold transition-colors hover:border-text-muted hover:text-text-primary">
              Back to Challenge Page
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">What Happens Next</span>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Join the community and look for the challenge welcome post.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Watch the quick orientation so the rules, daily rhythm, and first steps are clear.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Use the Day 1 resources to pick your project, choose your posting platform, and start moving.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10" data-tilt>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Check Your Email</span>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
              You should also receive challenge updates by email. If the email takes a few minutes, do not wait on it - the community is the main place to start.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/60 p-5">
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
                If you are not sure what to build yet, that is fine. The community resources are designed to help you get clarity before you start.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/dot-grid.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/magnetic.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/tilt.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
